post_text: Wouldn't your little ones be thrilled to have their favorite characters visit your neighborhood?!? Check in with Paulettes Princess Parties!
shared_text:
Paulettes Princess Parties
March 19 at 6:36 PM ·

In this time of unknown we want to reach out to neighborhoods to create joy and lots of smiles ! Singing , dancing , exercise and so much more !!! The Characters will be on you street while your children can be inside or in your front yard ! We will visit everyone participating! Check out our video with Rapunzel and Cinderella with details. All of our cast members are volunteering to bring Magical Moments . Donations are are welcome ! What you need to do :
* reach out to your neighbors
* choice a few options for date and times
* pick your characters up to three ( we are suggesting a princess and superhero , maybe a troll or descendant ? we have 80 characters and mascots)
* would love to have 20 house minimum , but we are so flexible!!!
* have a representative call the Fairy-Godmother , Paulette at 614-395-6330 to set up your very own Parade Party !!!!!!

We will become Part of your World and spread Magic..... Remember to put your colored pictures in your window or on your mailbox
